Polar Cursor Theme is a smooth and simple cursor set created primarily
in Inkscape. There are three cursor sets included in this package:

1) PolarCursorTheme (default): has orange busy cursors
2) PolarCursorTheme-Blue: blue variant
3) PolarCursorTheme-Green: green variant

NOTE:
The cursors are hosted at SourceForge by the SlackBuild maintainer.
